5000|$|Civil Aircraft Missile Protection System or CAMPS is an <b>infrared</b> <b>countermeasure</b> against infrared-homed {{anti-aircraft}} missiles, {{specifically designed}} to defend civilian aircraft flying under 15000 ft against MANPADS.|$|R
