5000|$|The Department of the Navy (DoN) also {{operates}} an <b>infrared</b> <b>countermeasures</b> {{program called}} LAIRCM, which is fielded exclusively on large fixed-wing aircraft, {{and uses a}} laser pointer-tracker to defeat IR-guided threats.|$|R
